in person more often...

458
00:24:10,080 --> 00:24:11,800
so that I can learn things from you.

459
00:24:12,170 --> 00:24:13,650
It shouldn't be a problem if I am free.

460
00:24:16,320 --> 00:24:19,800
Do you have a lover?

461
00:24:20,490 --> 00:24:22,210
Lover?

462
