624
00:34:46,469 --> 00:34:47,330
It depends.

625
00:34:47,409 --> 00:34:48,929
I shall keep you company.

626
00:34:49,250 --> 00:34:50,610
You are doing it right.

627
00:34:50,770 --> 00:34:52,330
